msgid "So you wanna buy a crab, eh. Well, first up you gotta have a solid crab care routine, let me tell you all about it..."
msgstr "所以你想買一隻螃蟹，呃。好吧，首先你必須有一個堅實的螃蟹護理程序，讓我告訴你所有關於它..."

#. Id: 65866-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 1.0
#. -- Parent line: 0 (65865-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Crab salesman
#: 65866-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Skip the chat. Let me see your crabs."
msgstr "免去聊天。讓我看看你的螃蟹。"

#. Id: 65869-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 2.0
#. -- Parent line: 1 (65866-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Crab salesman
#: 65869-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Can't let you walk away with one of my crabs until you learn the basics of good crab care..."
msgstr "在你學習好螃蟹護理的基礎知識之前，不能讓你帶走我的一隻螃蟹......"

