#. Id: 65870-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 2.0
#. -- Parent line: 1 (65867-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Crab salesman
#: 65870-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Now the crabs, see, they like fish, that's their favourite food. Otherwise they'll eat funghi, algae... you know, standard stuff. But you gotta make sure they eat five meals a day. And be warned, never feed them after sundown! NEVER!..."
msgstr "現在螃蟹，看，他們喜歡魚，這是他們最喜歡的食物。否則他們會吃真菌，藻類...你知道，標準的東西。但你必須確保他們每天吃五餐。並且要注意，日落之後永遠不要餵牠們！決不！..."

#. Id: 65871-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 3.0
#. -- Parent line: 2 (65870-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Crab salesman
#: 65871-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "It gives them indigestion. You've also gotta give them a ninety minute salt bath once a month so that they can molt no trouble. Now, they don't sleep well and they need affection, so make sure you sing 'em a song every night before bed, you gotta gurgle from the back of your throat, stroke his back legs too, he'll like that..."
msgstr "它給他們消化不良。你還必須每月給他們一次九十分鐘的鹽浴，這樣他們就可以毫無困難地熬夜。現在，他們睡不好，他們需要感情，所以一定要在睡覺前每晚唱一首歌，你要從喉嚨後面咕嚕咕嚕，撫摸他的後腿，他會喜歡那樣的...... 。"

#. Id: 65873-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 4.0
#. -- Parent line: 3 (65871-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Crab salesman
#: 65873-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "And don't work 'em too hard. They don't like conflict... sensitive creatures they are, put too much stress on 'em and they'll get depressed. Nothin' sadder than a bummed out crab."
msgstr "並且不要太努力工作。他們不喜歡衝突......他們是敏感的生物，對他們施加過多的壓力，他們會感到沮喪。沒什麼比一頭笨拙的螃蟹更難過。"

#. Id: 65872-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 5.0
#. -- Parent line: 4 (65873-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Crab salesman
#: 65872-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "... So, are you ready to become one with the crabs?"
msgstr "...那麼，你準備好與螃蟹成為一體了嗎？"

